SDS — Simple Design System

This project uses the SDS component library (@kzatsepin-xla/components).
Always import components from this package — never create custom versions of existing components.

Import pattern:

  // Individual component (tree-shakeable):
  import { Button } from '@kzatsepin-xla/components/ui/primitives/Button'

  // Or from root (all components):
  import { Button, Input, Dialog } from '@kzatsepin-xla/components'

Don't forget styles — add this import once in your root layout:

  import '@kzatsepin-xla/components/styles.css'

